name: Le Camping
tag_list: startup, seed-capital, accelerator, web, digital-natives, paris
overview:
Le Camping is leading the French ecosystem of innovation, providing seed capital and building high-growth web startups by means of and intensive 6-month program.

Le Camping is an initiative led by Silicon Sentier, that has been the hub for tech communities in Paris for 11 years.

Le Camping selects 12 young, scalable and ambitious startups. Technology, collaboration and fast development define the DNA of Le camping.

The first season showed great results: of the twelve start-ups, four raised funds and three did not require a round of fundraising.

The second season is starting in September 2011.
